\" src=\"http://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Accommodate-WordPress-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Accommodate-WordPress-Theme\" width=\"525\" height=\"855\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Accommodate-WordPress-Theme</p></div>\n<p>The <a title=\"Accommodate\" href=\"http://wplook.com/accommodate\" target=\"_blank\">Theme</a> looks beautiful at any size, be it a laptop screen, iPad, iPhone, Android Mobile or tablets.</p>\n<p><strong>Theme Features:</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"list_feature_news\">\n<li>Responsive design (Mobile first)</li>\n<li>Custom Post type menu</li>\n<li>Custom Logo</li>\n<li>Custom Background</li>\n<li>Custom CSS</li>\n<li>Custom Widgets</li>\n<li>Share Buttons</li>\n<li>Twitter Integration</li>\n<li>Nivo Slider <em>(a $19 value)</em></li>\n<li>SlidesJS</li>\n<li>Internationalized &amp; localization</li>\n<li>Multiple widget Areas</li>\n<li>Banners widget</li>\n<li>Twitter widget</li>\n<li>Flickr widget</li>\n<li>Drop-down Menu</li>\n<li>WordPress APIs respected</li>\n<li>Clean Code</li>\n<li>Microformats</li>\n<li>Cross-browser compatibility</li>\n<li>Threaded Comments</li>\n<li>Gravatar ready</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wplook/~4/y95k7o4x6Og\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"http://wplook.com/accommodate-hotel-wordpress-theme-1634.html/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"http://wplook.com/accommodate-hote