{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1609:\"<p>The week starts with a great news for you. It&#8217;s all about the launching of <a title=\"DailyPost PRO - Responsive WordPress Theme\" href=\"http://wplook.com/dailypost\">DailyPost PRO</a>.</p>\n<p>We care about our clients and we account for their wishes, that is why we thought that will be awesome to release the PRO version of DailyPost (<a title=\"See DailyPost Pro in action!\" href=\"http://demo.wplook.com/?themename=dailypostpro\" target=\"_blank\">see it in action</a>).<br />\n<span id=\"more-1383\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://demo.wplook.com/dailypostpro\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1399\" title=\"DailyPost PRO\" src=\"http://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/dailypost-pro.jpg\" alt=\"DailyPost PRO\" width=\"530\" height=\"507\" /></a></p>\n<p>The theme has new interesting features that will make your blog more useful:</p>\n<ul class=\"list_feature_news_full\">\n<li>Responsive design</li>\n<li>Custom Background</li>\n<li>Custom CSS</li>\n<li>Custom Widgets</li>\n<li>Share Buttons</li>\n<li>Twitter Integration</li>\n<li>Nivo Slider</li>\n<li>Internationalized &amp; localization</li>\n<li>Banners widget</li>\n<li>Tabs widget</li>\n<li>Twitter widget</li>\n<li>SEO Options Section</li>\n<li>Frequent theme upgrades</li>\n<li>WordPress APIs respected</li>\n<li>Clean Code</li>\n<li>Microformats</li>\n<li>Cross-browser compatibility</li>\n<li>Threaded Comments</li>\n<li>Gravatar ready</li>\n<li>Custom thumbnail images</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Hope you will enjoy it ans we wish you great start into the new week !</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wplook/~4/Cgf092j31Ys\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"http://wplook.com/dailypost-pro-released-1383.html/feed\";s:7: