s\">Custom Widgets</li>\n<li title=\"Share Buttons\">Share Buttons</li>\n<li title=\"Google Fonts\">Google Fonts</li>\n<li title=\"Twitter Integration\">Twitter Integration</li>\n<li title=\"jQuery UI image slide\">jQuery UI image slider</li>\n<li title=\"Nivo Slider\">Nivo Slider</li>\n<li title=\"Internationalized &amp; localization\">Internationalized &amp; localization</li>\n<li title=\"Multiple widget Areas\">Multiple widget Areas</li>\n<li title=\"Banners widget\">Banners widget</li>\n<li title=\"Social widget\">Social widget</li>\n<li title=\"Tabs widget\">Tabs widget</li>\n<li title=\"Twitter widget\">Twitter widget</li>\n<li title=\"Flickr widget\">Flickr widget</li>\n<li title=\"Drop-down Menu\">Drop-down Menu</li>\n<li title=\"SEO Options Section\">SEO Options Section</li>\n<li title=\"Frequent theme upgrades\">Frequent theme upgrades</li>\n<li title=\"WordPress APIs respected\">WordPress APIs respected</li>\n<li title=\"Clean Code\">Clean Code</li>\n<li title=\"Microformats\">Microformats</li>\n<li title=\"Cross-browser compatibility\">Cross-browser compatibility</li>\n<li title=\"Threaded Comments\">Threaded Comments</li>\n<li title=\"Gravatar ready\">Gravatar ready</li>\n<li title=\"Custom thumbnail images\">Custom thumbnail images</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wplook/~4/rlF_8H1oD8Y\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"http://wplook.com/chicstyle-a-new-and-modern-magazine-theme-1302.html/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http:/